       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. INTROLL2.
      * MONTHLY INTEREST POSTING WITH RULE TABLE INITIALIZATION.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-INTEREST-RULE-FLAG PIC X VALUE 'N'.
           88  INTEREST-RULE-ON VALUE 'Y'.
       01  WS-OUTSTANDING PIC 9(9)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-UNPAID-FEES PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-CREDITS      PIC 9(9)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-INT-BASE     PIC S9(9)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-APR          PIC 9(2)V99 VALUE 36.00.
       01  WS-INTEREST-AMT PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           PERFORM 1500-LOAD-INTEREST-RULE
           ACCEPT WS-OUTSTANDING
           ACCEPT WS-UNPAID-FEES
           ACCEPT WS-CREDITS
           IF INTEREST-RULE-ON
              COMPUTE WS-INT-BASE = WS-OUTSTANDING
                      - WS-UNPAID-FEES - WS-CREDITS
              IF WS-INT-BASE > ZERO
                 COMPUTE WS-INTEREST-AMT ROUNDED =
                         (WS-INT-BASE * WS-APR) / 1200
              END-IF
           END-IF
           DISPLAY 'INTEREST: ' WS-INTEREST-AMT
           STOP RUN.
       1500-LOAD-INTEREST-RULE.
           MOVE 'Y' TO WS-INTEREST-RULE-FLAG.
